# 🎯 If You Remember Only 5 Things...

1. Always write for users first.

2. Search Intent is more important than keyword stuffing.

3. Fast, mobile-friendly websites perform better.

4. Regularly monitor Google Search Console and GA4.

5. SEO is a long-term process that requires consistency.

